ass="zm-noti7-content-body"><div class="zm-noti7-popup-loading"><span class="noti-spinner-loading"></span></div></div></div></div></div><div class="zm-noti7-frame-border bottom"></div><div class="zm-noti7-popup-footer"><a href="/notifications" class="zm-noti7-popup-footer-all zg-right">查看全部 &raquo;</a><a href="/settings/notification" class="zm-noti7-popup-footer-set" title="通知设置" ><i class="zg-icon zg-icon-settings"></i></a></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="zu-global-notify" id="zh-global-message" style="display:none"><div class="zg-wrap"><div class="zu-global-nitify-inner"><a class="zu-global-notify-close" href="javascript:;" title="关闭" name="close">x</a><span class="zu-global-notify-icon"></span><span class="zu-global-notify-msg"></span></div></div></div><main class="pure-g receptacle"><section class="page-content-main pure-u-1 pure-u-md-17-24"><div class="unit-inner"><div class="module roundtable-profile clearfix"><a href="/roundtable/fenkai" class="photo visible-desktop"><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-25b83f019cc4e44d0ad1858d6ef2338c_xl.jpg" srcset="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-25b83f019cc4e44d0ad1858d6ef2338c_b.jpg 2x" alt="「分开」这件小事" class="avatar"></a><div class="content"><div class="title"><h1><a href="/roundtable/fenkai">「分开」这件小事</a></h1><span class="status">已结束</span></div><div class="description">毕业季，「分开」这件小事频繁地出现在我们的视线内：各赴前程与好友分开，面临异地与恋人分开，踏入职场与校园分开……随之而来的难过、迷茫、焦虑，该如何面对？
本期圆桌，让我们一起面对它 ：）</div><div class="actions"><button class="button-link share pull-left" data-id="284" data-token="fenkai"><i class="fi fi-share"></i>分享</button><span class="visits text-muted">84781633 次浏览 </span><span class="bull">&bull;</span><a href="/roundtable/fenkai/followers" class="followers text-muted"><span class="count" data-count="4571"> 4571</span> 人关注</a></div></div></div><div class="module"><ul class="menu-nav horizontal"><li class="active"><a href="/roundtable/fenkai">48 <span class="nowrap">条动态</span></a></li><li ><a href="/roundtable/fenkai/questions">34 <span class="nowrap">个问题</span></a></li><li ><a href="/roundtable/fenkai/comments">97 <span class="nowrap">条讨论</span></a></li></ul></div><div class="feeds loose"><ul class="items" data-paging="{&quot;next&quot;: &quot;/r/roundtables/fenkai/activities?offset=21&quot;}" data-navigable><li class="item" data-type="Answer"><a class="zg-anchor-hidden" name="answer-107421536"></a><link itemprop="url" href="/question/22977715/answer/425439106"><meta itemprop="question-id" content="1371900"><meta itemprop="question-url-token" content="22977715"><meta itemprop="answer-id" content="107421536"><meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="425439106"><div class="item-header"><h2 class="item-title"><a class="js-title-link" target="_blank" href="/question/22977715/answer/425439106">你认为离别时最伤感的话或者诗句是什么？</a></h2></div><article class="entry answer"><div class="entry-left hidden-phone"><a class="rating hidden-expanded js-expand js-vote-count" data-bind-votecount>1632</a><div class="votebar visible-expanded"><button class="up " title="赞同"><i class="fi-voteup-arrow"></i><span class="count">1632</span><span class="sr-only">赞同</span></button><button class="down" title="反对，不会显示你的姓名"><i class="fi-votedown-arrow"></i><span class="sr-only">反对，不会显示你的姓名</span></button></div></div><div class="entry-body"><div class="entry-meta"><strong class="author-line"><a class="author" href="/people/xiao-shi-9" data-hovercard='p$t$xiao-shi-9'>灯下说书人</a>，<span title="街边远行客，灯下说书人" class="bio">街边远行客，灯下说书人</span></strong></div><div class="entry-content js-collapse-body" data-author-name="灯下说书人" data-entry-url="/question/22977715/answer/425439106"><div class="summary hidden-expanded js-expand">「明日隔山岳，世事两茫茫。」 出自杜甫《赠卫八处士》，全诗如下： 人生不相见，动如参与商。今夕复何夕，共此灯烛光。少壮能几时，鬓发各已苍。访旧半为鬼，惊呼热中肠。焉知二十载，重上君子堂。昔别君未婚，儿女忽成行。怡然敬父执，问我来何方。问答乃…<a class="toggle-expand inline" href="/question/22977715/answer/425439106">显示全部</a></div><div class="visible-expanded"><div class="zm-item-vote-info" data-votecount="1632"><span class="voters"><span class="member"><a href="/people/zxy-1" data-hovercard='p$t$zxy-1'>zxy</a><span>、</span></span><span class="member"><a href="/people/jiang-jiang-67-37" data-hovercard='p$t$jiang-jiang-67-37'>山若昀海</a><span>、</span></span><span class="member"><a href="/people/liang-xx-0312" data-hovercard='p$t$liang-xx-0312'>静儿</a></span></span> <a class="more">等人赞同</a></div><script type="text" class="content"><p>「明日隔山岳，世事两茫茫。」</p><p><br></p><p>出自杜甫《赠卫八处士》，全诗如下：</p><p><br></p><p>人生不相见，动如参与商。</p><p>今夕复何夕，共此灯烛光。</p><p>少壮能几时，鬓发各已苍。</p><p>访旧半为鬼，惊呼热中肠。</p><p>焉知二十载，重上君子堂。</p><p>昔别君未婚，儿女忽成行。</p><p>怡然敬父执，问我来何方。</p><p>问答乃未已，驱儿罗酒浆。</p><p>夜雨剪春韭，新炊间黄粱。</p><p>主称会面难，一举累十觞。</p><p>十觞亦不醉，感子故意长。</p><p>明日隔山岳，世事两茫茫。</p><p><br></p><p>少时读诗，读到过这一首，当时一知半解，并不能真正体会其中的含义，年岁渐长，经历了很多分别，才慢慢懂了诗里无可奈何的悲伤。</p><p>最近整理旧物，翻到奶奶中学毕业时的纪念册，留下笔墨和照片的人们不是近百岁就是已经辞世。隔着时光和被蠹虫咬出的孔洞都能感受到一种郑重。奶奶给我讲过当年她作为女生班长奔走校园找老师校长题词的旧事，仿佛能透过纪念册里那张勤恳而热切的少女脸庞看到当年的场景。</p><p>（多图预警）</p><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-24ee32dd63a282a66ff1f4ad07415b12_b.jpg" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="3264" data-rawheight="2448" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-4fa676a0dccfd6034d49f91646736a66_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="3264" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-24ee32dd63a282a66ff1f4ad07415b12_r.jpg"><figcaption>初中毕业纪念册 封面为手绣</figcaption></figure><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-47441c5c46c0f3931cd6bc25dc803d41_b.jpg" data-