桌」？如何参与</a>？<br>圆桌页面：<a href="http://www.zhihu.com/roundtable" data-editable="true" data-title="活动">活动列表</a></p></div></li></ul></div></div><div class="module guests"><div class="module-header"><h3>嘉宾</h3></div><div class="module-body"><ul class="items"><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/liu-xiang-yu-66-81" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$liu-xiang-yu-66-81'><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-18408a74f185e0532fdb9575f298341f_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="暗涌"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/roundtable/fenkai/liu-xiang-yu-66-81/answers" class="answers text-muted">1 个回答</a><a class="name author-link" href="/people/liu-xiang-yu-66-81" data-hovercard='p$t$liu-xiang-yu-66-81'>暗涌</a><span class="icon icon-badge-best_answerer icon-badge" data-tooltip="s$b$优秀回答者"></span><div class="bio">The Follower of Psychology</div></div></div></li><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/lingjun-chen" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$lingjun-chen'><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-b0e9b980d771adf8f6323b65bafde90b_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="陈凌隽"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/roundtable/fenkai/lingjun-chen/answers" class="answers text-muted">3 个回答</a><a class="name author-link" href="/people/lingjun-chen" data-hovercard='p$t$lingjun-chen'>陈凌隽</a><span class="icon icon-badge-identity icon-badge" data-tooltip="s$b$已认证的个人"></span><div class="bio">宾夕法尼亚大学 (University of Pennsylvania) <span class="bull">&bull;</span> 发展心理学博士在读</div></div></div></li><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/xiao-shi-9" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$xiao-shi-9'><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/4b46f2b7f_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="灯下说书人"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/roundtable/fenkai/xiao-shi-9/answers" class="answers text-muted">2 个回答</a><a class="name author-link" href="/people/xiao-shi-9" data-hovercard='p$t$xiao-shi-9'>灯下说书人</a><div class="bio">cons